Localization.Name: Terra Liberty Ale (Bottle)
Localization.Description:
HEI: 23
Effects: Cognitive Impairment, Dehydrating

Liberty Lake beer has been brewed by families on Terra for generations to provide a crisp, clean ale perfect to partake when you arrive at those little moments made to be spent enjoying life. Terra Liberty is hop forward with a crisp finish.
